[China's promise, as expressed in the last passage, is reflected in
today's 5th follow-up report to the OIE, referring to mortalities in
chickens, magpies and "other kinds of wild birds", caused by H5
Subtype Avian Influenza in Badaohao, Jinzhou city, Liaoning province.
<http://oie.int/downld/AVIAN%20INFLUENZA/China%20Follow-up%20report%20No5.pdf>.

